<glossary>
<definition id="fs-id1172100667579">
<term>free electrons</term>
<meaning id="fs-id1172098660308">also called conduction electrons, these are the electrons in a conductor that are not bound to any particular atom, and hence are free to move around</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>

